RSEM RNA-seq Pipeline
=================================

1) Already built Rsem Genomes
-----------------------------

hg19_ucsc_fil: hg19 ucsc genome (filtering extra chromosomes).

hg19_ensembl_fil: hg19 Ensemble genome (filtering extra chromosomes).


2) Build New Rsem Genomes:
----------------------------


3) Aligning Reads to Genome:
----------------------------

Script: rsem-align.pl 
 
Edit align.cfg file for setting the parameters

Type perl rsem-align.pl for usage 


4) Consolidate Counts (gene/isoforms) into a data matrix
--------------------------------------------------------

Script: rsem_consolidate.pl

Type perl rsem_consolidate.pl for usage and parameters.



5) Get Description for Gene/Isoform Ids in Data Matrix output
---------------------------------------------------------------

script : rsem_getDesc.pl



6) Differential Gene Expression
----------------------------------


